    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《荒野猎人》</strong>是一款硬核回合制生存故事生成游戏，并融入策略元素。躲避毒雾，与变异生物战斗，努力保命。为生存而战，消灭变异生物，避开感染区域，证明你的实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索残酷的开放世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在自动或手动模式下搜索住宅楼、商店、汽车和药房。寻找武器、装备、补给——一切能帮助你生存的东西。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/208d5d619c911240081eb85da741b8f1.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/208d5d619c911240081eb85da741b8f1.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/208d5d619c911240081eb85da741b8f1.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为生存而战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在途中遇到许多变异敌人，你必须不惜一切代价消灭它们。你能应付吗？还是他们会更强大？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/66357fa2d9bf4c91d68f1c2fd3abbe72.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/66357fa2d9bf4c91d68f1c2fd3abbe72.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/66357fa2d9bf4c91d68f1c2fd3abbe72.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >努力生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >密切关注你队伍的生命体征：健康、饱腹感、口渴感、能量、辐射水平。如果他们的水平降至临界值，你就会轻易成为猎物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/60af5284f3a6ed7afc390a25aa52857d.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/60af5284f3a6ed7afc390a25aa52857d.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/60af5284f3a6ed7afc390a25aa52857d.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离酸雾</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浏览全球地图，尽一切可能避免遭遇放射性雾。你无法在一个地方久留。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/d72ac076017dc2fed3fb269917fcf9f8.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/d72ac076017dc2fed3fb269917fcf9f8.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/d72ac076017dc2fed3fb269917fcf9f8.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种类繁多的武器，从自制长矛到霰弹枪，你一定能找到你喜欢的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/ca1edb638f35b613daee1b01864f145c.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/ca1edb638f35b613daee1b01864f145c.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/ca1edb638f35b613daee1b01864f145c.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集物品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你无法带走所有找到的东西——你只能带走最必需的东西。分发库存中的物品，尝试组合收集的材料并创建新物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/abf9528d67f8b215a9f6526ffd9ad3df.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/abf9528d67f8b215a9f6526ffd9ad3df.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/abf9528d67f8b215a9f6526ffd9ad3df.mp4?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/75a01d3bba468006b82af4830f9c3b0c.poster.avif?t=1770177491\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286430/extras/75a01d3bba468006b82af4830f9c3b0c.webm?t=1770177491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
